        "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64\nOffice Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT\nTO : THE DIRECTOR DATE: July 12, 1949\nFROM : D. M. Ladd\nSUBJECT:\nYou inquired as to what was being done with\nreference to the information concerning flying saucers,"
